# 凉拌茄子
“Liang ban” Eggplant (Cold and dressed eggplant)

0:00:04.880,0:00:07.140
# 首先我们准备嫩茄子2根
First, prepare 2 tender eggplants

0:00:07.140,0:00:09.100
# 将茄子头转动的方式切下
Cut off the stem while rotating the eggplant

0:00:09.100,0:00:11.600
# 同学们茄子蒂也是可以食用的
Please be noted that the stem can be eaten as well #请检查stem

0:00:17.300,0:00:19.280
# 然后将其对半切开备用
Then cut the eggplant into two halves

0:00:19.280,0:00:22.200
# 将茄子从中间切开之后再切成小条备用
cut them in the middle and then into small strips

0:00:23.595,0:00:25.855
# 茄子切好之后放入盆中备用
Put the eggplant into a bowl for further use

0:00:25.860,0:00:27.080
# 下一步开始处理
Next, process the eggplant

0:00:27.080,0:00:29.020
# 盆中加入食用盐1勺（约2克）
Add one spoon of salt into the bowl (about 2 grams)

0:00:29.020,0:00:32.115
# 然后加入适量的清水和白醋浸泡10分钟备用
Then add some water and white vinegar to soak the eggplant for 10 minutes

0:00:32.115,0:00:34.825
# 这一步的目的是防止茄子氧化变黑
The purpose of this step is to prevent the eggplant from blackening due to oxidation

0:00:42.340,0:00:45.520
# 10分钟之后将茄子放入蒸锅中开中火蒸20分钟
10 minutes later, put the eggplant into a steamer. Steam it for 20 minutes with medium heat

0:00:45.640,0:00:47.720
# 这一步的目的是将茄子蒸制熟透
The purpose of this step is to fully steam the eggplant

0:00:47.960,0:00:50.760
# 嫌麻烦的同学也可以直接下锅煮20分钟
If you prefer a simpler procedure, you can directly boil the eggplant for 20 minutes

0:00:50.880,0:00:52.900
